{"tid":1928723,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲試過梨狀肌症候群(pyriformis syndrome)","createTime":"2020-03-16T14:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:52:49.000Z","uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc91403ecad5229cfda430da1b2c9ddf11e16b7","tid":1928723,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"最後腰對落果個位好痛<br />\n著褲唔可以正常著 <br />\n一R 後個人就痛 （做squat 會痛）<br />\n成個人摺唔埋<br />\n起身同坐低都會痛<br />\n都痛左超過一星期<br />\n上網自己睇懷疑係梨狀肌症候群(pyriformis syndrome)<br />\n有冇巴絲試過？ 最後點樣好返？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968312e1ad3037e27f0a833a2a80975f8ab41429","tid":1928723,"uid":111615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"唔好懷疑啦, 搵醫生照咗先，確認咗邊度問題先，點醫都係後話。"},{"pid":"25047257dc7d338e42b172339be91b0525a65368","tid":1928723,"uid":271462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:46:20.000Z","msg":"可大可小<br />\n小事: 梨狀肌症候群 - 睇骨科, 轉去物理治療<br />\n大事: 椎間盤突出 - 骨科手術移除突出椎間盤 / 密集式物理治療 (保守治療)<br />\n<br />\n利申:<br />\nL4-L5 &amp; L5-S1 Disk Dislocation 椎間盤突出<br />\n冇開刀, 捱左一年物理治療再抖一年先做到運動<br />\n<br />\n有段時間痛到想自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絲打快啲去睇orth骨科<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b207cd3f7710d6bb8ff63fedd313ed858b45dd","tid":1928723,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25047257dc7d338e42b172339be91b0525a65368","tid":1928723,"uid":271462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:46:20.000Z","msg"